## 🧰 Tech Stack

| Technology | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| **Frontend** | React.js, Tailwind CSS *(if used)* |
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express.js |
| **Database** | MongoDB with Mongoose |
| **Authentication** | JWT (JSON Web Tokens) |
| **Hosting** | Firebase (Frontend) & Render (Backend) |

